  "title": "Out, Damned Spot",
  "description": "Out, Damned Spot is a punk rock Macbeth musical packed with glitter, blood, rebellion, and witchy power! Lady M and her witches battle Duncan the Condo King to save New Birnam Wood from development. Pole dancing, mushroom trips, and prophecy collide in this wild ride starring climate activist Everrr Andra. Long live the queen!",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Kirsten Ruško + Jillian Maguire<br><strong>Director</strong>: Dr. Baddy<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Everrr Andra, Dr. Baddy, Jillian Maguire + Kirsten Ruško<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Everrr Andra<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Kirsten Rusko<br/></br>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/mouthybitchproductions",
  "plain_language": "Out, Damned Spot A punk rock prophecy soaked in glitter, blood, and rebellion. Lady M and her witches are out to save New Birnam Wood from the greedy clutches of Duncan the Condo King and his bro brigade. Featuring pole dancing, psychedelic mushroom trips, and a whole lot of murder, this riotous reimagining of Macbeth gives Lady M her due. Starring real-life climate activist Everrr Andra, Out, Damned Spot is a spellbinding mix of protest, punk, and prophecy.",
